title: ee-cptcity
text: Cptcity solium platform can find multiple colour palettes various themes related cartography, technical illustration design. archive supports various formats organised author. Cptcity currently colour palettes popular desktop Geographic Information Systems QGIS, GRASS , SAGA , ARCGIS , others. Currently, 7000 colour palettes, however second version ee-cptcity module 300 colour palettes incorporated along 2 popular palettes like rocket , mako turbo.
